data.description: This beautiful Arthur Rutenberg pool home could be yours.  With 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, there is room for your growing or blended family.  The 4th bedroom and one of the baths is set apart from the others, making a perfect opportunity for a mother-in-law or teen suite.  Open the doors from the living room, family room, breakfast nook and master bedroom to the lanai/pool area and create the perfect home for entertaining.  The lanai/pool area has vinyl sliding doors (for those few cool nights) and an outdoor kitchen.  The 3-car garage means room for all your vehicles or toys.  There is a large air-conditioned closet in the garage area for those things that you don't want to store into a hot attic. The back yard is fenced, making a great place for kids or pets to run.  The whole-house (propane) generator keeps you from spending any time in the dark.  All openings are protected by accordion-type storm shutters. Make your appointment to see this move-in ready home today.
